  <para style="p">
    <verse number="17" style="v" sid="JOB 15:17" />Je vais t’instruire, écoute-moi ; je <char style="w" strong="H5608">raconterai</char> <char style="w" strong="H2088">ce</char> <char style="w" strong="H8085">que</char> j’ai <char style="w" strong="H2372">vu</char>, <verse eid="JOB 15:17" /><verse number="18" style="v" sid="JOB 15:18" /><char style="w" strong="H5046">ce</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">les</char> <char style="w" strong="H2450">sages</char> enseignent, — ils <char style="w" strong="H3808">ne</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">le</char> cachent <char style="w" strong="H3808">pas</char>, l’ayant <char style="w" strong="H5046">appris</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">de</char> <char style="w" strong="H5046">leurs</char> pères ; <verse eid="JOB 15:18" /><verse number="19" style="v" sid="JOB 15:19" /><char style="w" strong="H5414">à</char> eux seuls avait été <char style="w" strong="H5414">donné</char> <char style="w" strong="H5414">le</char> pays, <char style="w" strong="H5674">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H8432">parmi</char> eux <char style="w" strong="H3808">jamais</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">ne</char> <char style="w" strong="H5674">passa</char> l’étranger. — <verse eid="JOB 15:19" /><verse number="20" style="v" sid="JOB 15:20" />« <char style="w" strong="H3117">Le</char> <char style="w" strong="H7563">méchant</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3117">durant</char> <char style="w" strong="H3605">tous</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">ses</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">jours</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3117">est</char> rongé <char style="w" strong="H3117">par</char> l’angoisse ; <char style="w" strong="H3117">un</char> petit <char style="w" strong="H4557">nombre</char> d’années <char style="w" strong="H7563">sont</char> <char style="w" strong="H6845">réservées</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">à</char> l’oppresseur. <verse eid="JOB 15:20" /><verse number="21" style="v"