rong="H6310">bouche</char> <char style="w" strong="H7307">de</char> Dieu. <verse eid="JOB 15:30" /><verse number="31" style="v" sid="JOB 15:31" />Qu’il n’espère rien <char style="w" strong="H8582">du</char> <char style="w" strong="H7723">mensonge</char>, il y <char style="w" strong="H1961">sera</char> pris ; <char style="w" strong="H1961">le</char> <char style="w" strong="H7723">mensonge</char> <char style="w" strong="H1961">sera</char> <char style="w" strong="H1961">sa</char> <char style="w" strong="H8545">récompense</char>. <verse eid="JOB 15:31" /><verse number="32" style="v" sid="JOB 15:32" />Elle <char style="w" strong="H4390">arrivera</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">avant</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">ses</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">jours</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">soient</char> <char style="w" strong="H4390">pleins</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3117">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">son</char> <char style="w" strong="H3712">rameau</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">ne</char> <char style="w" strong="H7488">verdira</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">plus</char>. <verse eid="JOB 15:32" /><verse number="33" style="v" sid="JOB 15:33" />Il secouera, comme <char style="w" strong="H7993">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H1612">vigne</char>, <char style="w" strong="H1612">son</char> fruit <char style="w" strong="H7993">à</char> peine éclos ; il laissera <char style="w" strong="H7993">tomber</char> <char style="w" strong="H7993">sa</char> <char style="w" strong="H5328">fleur</char>, comme l’olivier. <verse eid="JOB 15:33" /><verse number="34" style="v" sid="JOB 15:34" /><char style="w" strong="H3588">Car</char> <char style="w" strong="H3588">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H5712">maison</char> <char style="w" strong="H5712">de</char> l’impie est <char style="w" strong="H1565">stérile</char>, <char style="w" strong="H7810">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H5712">le</char> f