  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v" sid="JOB 32:11" />J’ai <char style="w" strong="H3176">attendu</char> <char style="w" strong="H5704">tant</char> <char style="w" strong="H1697">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H1697">vous</char> parliez, j’ai prêté l’oreille <char style="w" strong="H5704">à</char> vos <char style="w" strong="H8394">raisonnements</char>, jusqu’à <char style="w" strong="H1697">la</char> fin <char style="w" strong="H1697">de</char> vos débats. <verse eid="JOB 32:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="JOB 32:12" />Je vous ai suivis attentivement, <char style="w" strong="H6030">et</char> nul n’a <char style="w" strong="H3198">convaincu</char> Job, nul d’entre vous n’a <char style="w" strong="H6030">réfuté</char> <char style="w" strong="H6030">ses</char> paroles. <verse eid="JOB 32:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="JOB 32:13" /><char style="w" strong="H3808">Ne</char> dites <char style="w" strong="H3808">pas</char> : « Nous avons <char style="w" strong="H4672">trouvé</char> <char style="w" strong="H4672">la</char> <char style="w" strong="H2451">sagesse</char> ; c’est Dieu qui <char style="w" strong="H4672">le</char> frappe, <char style="w" strong="H3808">et</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">non</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">pas</char> l’homme. » <verse eid="JOB 32:13" /><verse number="14" style="v" sid="JOB 32:14" /><char style="w" strong="H7725">Il</char> n’a <char style="w" strong="H3808">pas</char> <char style="w" strong="H7725">dirigé</char> contre moi <char style="w" strong="H7725">ses</char> <char style="w" strong="H4405">discours</char>, mais ce n’est <char style="w" strong="H3808">pas</char> <char style="w" strong="H7725">avec</char> <char style="w" strong="H7725">vos</char> <char style="w" strong="H4405">paroles</char> <char style="w" strong="H3808">que</char> <char style="w" strong="H7725">je</char> lui <char style="w" strong="H7725">répondrai</char>.<verse eid="JOB 32:14" /></para>
